Package: BootCV
Title: Bootstrapping the Cross-Validation Estimate
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Yuanhui", "Luo", role = c("aut", "cre"), email="yluocl@connect.ust.hk"), 
	     person("Bryan", "Cai", role = c("aut")))
Description: Provide fast bootstrap methods to quantify the uncertainty of cross-validation estimate, which quickly estimates the standard error of the cross-validation estimate and produces valid confidence intervals for a population parameter measuring average model performance.
